title: Keep it Handy Leather Polishing Wipes (Pack of 8)
description: Product Description Keep it Handy Leather wipes are large, strong and convenient to use. The non-bleach formula offers effective hygenic cleaning with a pleasant fragrance. Use on all leather surfaces. Ingredients Nonionic surfactants <5%, Ampohoteric surfactants <5%, Preservatives: Methylparaben, propylparaben, diazolidinyl urea; Perfume: Limonene Directions 1. Pull back the resealable cover and pull out the wipe. 2. Surfaces may vary in quality, therefore suitability should be checked by using first on a small inconspicuous area. 3. Wipe surfaces evenly to remove grime and dirt and kill bacteria. 4. Allow surfaces to dry. No need to rinse. 5. Re-seal pack to prevent wipes drying out. Dispose of wipe in waste bin (do not flush down the toilet). Important: Use every wipe once and on one surface to to reduce the spread of bacteria. Safety Warning Keep our of reach of children. For household cleaning only. In case of accidental contact with eyes, rinse immediately with plenty of water. Seek medical attention if irritation persists. Wash and dry hands after use. See more
